---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Top 10 Plant Extracts for Skincare in 2024 | Benefits & Applications"
  description="Discover the most effective plant extracts for skincare products. Learn their benefits, applications, and how to choose the right extracts for your cosmetic formulations."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Top 10 Plant Extracts for Skincare in 2024</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">Natural plant extracts are the fastest growing ingredients in cosmetic formulations. Discover which extracts are trending this year and their benefits for skin.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">1. Grape Seed Extract (95% OPC)</h2>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl">🍇</span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Key Benefit: Powerful antioxidant, anti-aging</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Active ingredient: Proanthocyanidins (OPC)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Grape seed extract is one of the most popular anti-aging ingredients in skincare. OPCs are 20x more powerful than vitamin C and 50x more powerful than vitamin E in neutralizing free radicals that cause skin aging.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Applications:</strong> Anti-aging serums, moisturizers, eye creams, sun care products</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">2. Green Tea Extract (98% EGCG)</h2>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl">🍵</span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Key Benefit: Anti-inflammatory, antioxidant, soothing</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Active ingredient: Epigallocatechin Gallate (EGCG)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Green tea extract is perfect for sensitive and acne-prone skin. EGCG reduces redness and inflammation, soothes irritated skin, and protects against UV damage.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Applications:</strong> Acne treatments, soothing creams, after-sun products, anti-aging formulations</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">3. Aloe Vera Extract</h2>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl">🌵</span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Key Benefit: Moisturizing, soothing, healing</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Active ingredients: Polysaccharides, vitamins, amino acids</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Aloe vera is a classic skincare ingredient with excellent moisturizing and healing properties. It hydrates the skin without leaving a greasy residue, accelerates wound healing, and soothes sunburn.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Applications:</strong> Moisturizers, after-sun products, face masks, acne treatments, baby care products</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">4. Centella Asiatica Extract</h2>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl">🍀</span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Key Benefit: Skin barrier repair, anti-inflammatory, wound healing</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Active ingredients: Asiaticoside, Madecassoside</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Centella asiatica extract is extremely popular in Korean skincare formulations. It strengthens the skin barrier, reduces transepidermal water loss, and promotes collagen production. Perfect for sensitive and damaged skin.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Applications:</strong> Barrier repair creams, sensitive skin products, anti-aging serums, post-treatment care</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">5. Turmeric Extract (95% Curcumin)</h2>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl">🌿</span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Key Benefit: Brightening, anti-inflammatory, antioxidant</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Active ingredient: Curcumin</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Turmeric extract is excellent for brightening dull skin and reducing hyperpigmentation. Its powerful anti-inflammatory properties also help calm acne-prone skin and reduce redness.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Applications:</strong> Brightening serums, face masks, acne treatments, even-toning products</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-green-200 mt-12">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-4">High-Quality Plant Extracts for Your Cosmetic Formulations</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Weiyijie Bio supplies a full range of cosmetic grade plant extracts with 99%+ purity, complete certifications, and small MOQ support. All our extracts are tested for purity and heavy metals before shipment.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">100+ cosmetic grade plant extracts available</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">COA, TDS, MSDS documents provided for every product</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">1kg MOQ, perfect for formulation testing</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Custom specifications and packaging available</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="text-center">
          <a href="/category/cosmetic-ingredients" class="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-2 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all mr-4">
            View All Cosmetic Ingredients
          </a>
          <a href="/#contact" class="bg-white border-2 border-green-600 hover:bg-green-50 text-green-600 font-semibold px-6 py-2 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all">
            Request Free Samples
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
